Liverpool will take on Flamengo in the final of the Club World Cup on Saturday. The Reds battled to a 2-1 win over Monterrey to book their spot. Copa Libertadores winners Flamengo secured their place, with a 3-1 comeback victory over Al Hilal. Kick-off is 6.30 pm West African time. Liverpool XI vs. Flamengo: Alisson; Alexander-Arnold, Gomez, Van Dijk, Robertson; Henderson, Keita, Oxlade-Chamberlain; Salah, Firmino, Mane Flamengo XI vs Liverpool: Diego Alves; Rafinha Caio Mari Filipe Luís; Willian Arão Gerson; Ribeiro De Arrascaeta Henrique; Gabriel Saturday, December 21
